<body>
<h2 id="imagekeys">Image Control Keys </h2>
<table>
<th>Keys</th><th>Effect</th>
<tr><td>d</td><td>Measure Distance - press d then left click and drag mouse between points</td></tr>
<tr><td>h</td><td>Show/Hide EM Image (toggle)</td></tr>
<tr><td>k</td><td>If look ahead is on - chose new look ahead distances</td></tr>
<tr><td>l</td><td>Look ahead (Toggle). When switching it on, choose no. of look-ahead planes</td></tr>
<tr><td>q</td><td>Hide/Show Frame No. (toggle)</td></tr>
<tr><td>z</td><td>Reset display</td></tr>
<tr><td>F1</td><td>Help</td></tr>
<tr><td>F6</td><td>Display Scale Bar (size in nm) (toggle)</td></tr>
<tr><td>F8</td><td>Change palette</td></tr>
<tr><td>F12</td><td>Flip Image around Y axis</td></tr>
<tr><td>+</td><td>Zoom In</td></tr>
<tr><td>-</td><td>Zoom Out</td></tr>
<tr><td>Home</td><td>move image to first plane</td></tr>
<tr><td>End</td><td>move image to last plane</td></tr>
<tr><td>Esc</td><td>Quit program</td></tr>
<tr><td>Arrow keys</td><td>&larr; image 1 plane back, &rarr; image 1 plane forward</td></tr>
<tr><td>Press L mouse<br>button and move<br>mouse</td><td>move left &rArr; planes back; move right &rArr; planes forward</td></tr>  
</table>
<p>Many of the above can be accessed through the menu (mouse right click)</p>
</body>